{
  "text": "The results largely fell within the ranges shown for the city centers of Canberra, Sydney, Los Angles, and Addis Ababa in Figure 3 of [CITATION_1] ; i.e. between 2 and 10 mW/m 2 (which translates to 0.2-1 \u00b5W/cm 2 ). However, two specific hot spots gave cause for concern.",
